    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just about balance. it feels like the more i need, the more i'm taking away from them. they have their own lives, their own stress. i look at them and i just see how much weight i'm adding to their shoulders. it's like i'm just a problem they have to solve every single day.",
